                    Your menu must be nice but at the same time profitable and workable for
                    bartenders to make all the drinks as fast as possible.
                    <br>
                    Many bartenders have no idea what they're doing when making the bar list without
                    thinking about service time, profit, or even worse, cost of products.
                    <br>
                    They just make whatever and guess where all of this will end? Slow service, low
                    profit, waste of money, service burnout, and so on.
                    <br>
                    I can make very good drinks thinking about guests target, Drinks design, speed
